<section id="photographer_outer" class="big_wrapper">
  <div class="wrapper" id="photographer">
    <div class="key_point">
      <h1>
      Bring home your personal photographer
      </h1>
      <p>
      Pikmoments is a smart camera that can automatically take amazing photographs and short videos at the right moment. Just install it on your wall or table, and it will use intelligent algorithms to understand when you are smiling or laughing, and will capture those moments for you.
      <p>
    </div>
    <div class="key_point_image">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="phoneAndSocial_outer" class="big_wrapper">
  <div class="wrapper" id="phoneAndSocial">
    <div class="key_point">
      <h1>
        Photos delivered directly to your phone
      </h1>
      <p>
      We know you are always on the move, so we make sure you don't miss the good things happening at home. Pikmoments will send the photos it is taking at home, instantly to your phone so you are always connected to your home, people and pets. You can store these photos to your phone, or share them with friends.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="key_point_image">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="crystal_clear_outer" class="big_wrapper">
  <div class="wrapper" id="crystal_clear">
    <div class="key_point">
      <h1>
      5MP camera to capture crystal clear photographs
      </h1>
      <p>
     Pikmoments uses a 5MP camera with auto-focus, so your photos are always sharp and amazing. It also has a 180 degree field of view, so you can place the device anywhere in the room, without having to think a bit.
      <p>
    </div>
    <div class="key_point_image">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="portable_outer" class="big_wrapper">
  <div class="battery_animation">
    <%= image_tag("keypointImages/green.png", :id =>"full") %>
  </div>
  <div class="wrapper" id="portable">
    <div class="key_point">
      <h1>
        Super portable. Up to 20 hours battery life.
      </h1>
      <p>
        Hang it on the wall, or keep it on the desk. The device is amazingly portable, with a 20hrs battery life. So, just charge it once before going to sleep.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="key_point_image">
      <div class="hours_animation">
        <div id="battery_hours">1</div>
        <div id="battery_hours_label">Hrs</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="cloud_outer" class="big_wrapper">
  <div class="wrapper" id="cloud">
    <div class="key_point">
      <h1>
        Wireless connectivity with cloud backup of moments
      </h1>
      <p>
        Using 802.11 bgn wireless networking, your device is always connected to the internet,so your photos are sent to you in real time through the cloud.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="key_point_image">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="secure_outer" class="big_wrapper">
  <div class="wrapper" id="secure">
    <div class="key_point">
      <h1>
        All images, safe and secure
      </h1>
      <p>
        Nobody other than you has access to your images. We understand that this is about your loved ones and we take their privacy a little too seriously.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="key_point_image">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
